OL,3,CTwo men found guilty of murder of
OL,4,CAndrew Main in Swansea
OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder of 33-year-old Andrew Main in
OL,8,FSwansea city centre last year.
OL,10,F26-year-old Joseph Dix, from Frome,
OL,11,FSomerset, and 28-year-old Macauley
OL,12,FRuddock, from Bath, Somerset, both
OL,13,Fpleaded not guilty to murder following
OL,14,Fthe incident, which took place on
OL,15,FPrincess Way on July 17, 2024.
OL,17,FAndrew Main, from Falkirk, Scotland,
OL,18,Fdied from his injuries on August 14
OL,19,Fhaving never regained consciousness.
