OL,3,CTwo men found guilty of murder of
OL,4,CAndrew Main in Swansea
OL,6,FAll three were visiting the area for
OL,7,Fwork, staying at the same hotel in the
OL,8,Fcity centre, and met for the first
OL,9,Ftime at a nearby bar.
OL,11,FLater that night, an argument broke
OL,12,Fout back at the hotel between Joseph
OL,13,FDix and Macauley Ruddock and Andrew
OL,14,FMain and his friend Michael Bell.
OL,16,FThis argument moved onto the street,
OL,17,Fbefore Dix and Ruddock chased after
OL,18,FAndrew Main, ultimately striking him
OL,19,Funconscious before carrying out a
OL,20,Fsustained attack.
