OL,3,CTwo men found guilty of murder of
OL,4,CAndrew Main in Swansea
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Claire Lamerton
OL,7,Ffrom South Wales Police said "while
OL,8,Fthe parties had all consumed alcohol
OL,9,Fthat night, that does not provide an
OL,10,Fexcuse for the level of violence
OL,11,Fdisplayed by Joseph Dix and Macauley
OL,12,FRuddock.
OL,14,F"They clearly set out to cause serious
OL,15,Finjury to their victim, and now will
OL,16,Fface significant prison sentences for
OL,17,Ftheir actions.
