OL,3,CTwo men found guilty of murder of
OL,4,CAndrew Main in Swansea
OL,6,F"This case highlights how the effects
OL,7,Fof intoxicants can negatively affect
OL,8,Fbehaviour and decision-making. Had
OL,9,FJoseph Dix and Macauley Ruddock chosen
OL,10,Fto walk away that night, a life would
OL,11,Fhave been saved, and they would not be
OL,12,Fconvicted killers."
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain with Andrew's
OL,15,Ffamily and friends, who have been
OL,16,Fdevastated by what has happened and
OL,17,Fcontinue to grieve his loss.
